The commands are basically:

{code}
cmake -DCMAKE_EXPORT_COMPILE_COMMANDS=ON ..
iwyu_tool.py -p . > iwyu.txt
{code}

This assumes that the IWYU binary is in your PATH. You have to build the branch of IWYU that matches the version of clang in use: https://github.com/include-what-you-use/include-what-you-use/tree/clang_6.0
